Actor Alex Ekubo has undoubtedly has explained the many opportunities his career affords him .
The talented actor, who is currently on a movie set in Cameroon, also utilized the opportunity to learn a thing or two about their culture and try out new dishes. According to Ekubo, he loves the fact the job offers him the opportunity to experience the world, meet people and have a feel different interesting things. Speaking further, Alex noted Cameroon has be fun as he has enjoyed his stay there Sharing a photo of himself and crew on Instagram, he wrote; “Filming has blessed me with the amazing opportunity to travel the world, meet new people, learn new culture & try out new food. I completely love it. Cameroon has been a blast.”